<i>noun</i>: 산 [산] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square"><li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>산 [산]</dt><br>
<dd>acid</dd><br>
<dd>물에 녹았을 때 수소 이온을 내 놓으며, 염기와 만나면 중화하는 물질.</dd><br>
<dd>A substance that produces a hydrogen ion when dissolved in water, and is neutralized when combined with a base.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>